title: Молодёжка. Новая смена
overview: The Polytech Sharks Student Hockey League team is on the verge of disbanding. But Kazantsev comes to the university, who decides to turn the Sharks into the best team in the league and thereby increase the rating of the institute. He sees the former Bears player Andrei Kislyak as the club's coach first of all. To take the Sharks to the next level, Kislyak will not only have to find a common language with a new generation of athletes, but also change himself.
